init_text: When you die, you appear in a cinema with a number of other people who look like you. You find out that they are your previous reincarnations, and soon you all begin watching your next life on the big screen.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You see yourself as a young man or woman, and you see your future self as an old man or woman.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You see the people you will meet and the places you will go.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You see the things you will do and the things that will be done to you.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You see the things that you have done in your past lives and the things that you have not done.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You see the things that you have learned and the things that you have not learned.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You see how you could have done things differently.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: After you have watched your life, you are asked to choose what you want to do with your next life.

actions.name: text-delete
actions.text: There is no consequences to your choice

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You are locked into that choice.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I would like to be a hero.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: If reincarnation is real, then I will get the chance to live a life where I am a hero.
